text: Aziz el Khanchaf (born 25 August 1977 in Orléans, France) is a Moroccan-French football player, he currently plays for UR La Louvière Centre in Belgium. ==Career== El Khanchaf also played for Stade Lavallois (1996–2000), ES Wasquehal (2000–2002), RC Paris (2002–2005), KSK Ronse (2005–2006), RAEC Mons (2006–2008), KV Red Star Waasland Beveren (2008–2009) Boussu Dour Borinage (2009-2010), UR Louvière Centre (2011-2015) ===Position=== He plays in the offensive midfield. ==External links== * Profile Category:Living people Category:1977 births Category:French footballers Category:French people of Moroccan descent Category:Stade Lavallois players Category:Racing Club de France Football players Category:R.A.E.C.
